txt.en: 'I shall rally others to our cause...destroy these foul invaders.'
'Why must I suffer these interruptions? Do you not realize that you are but puppets in my hand?'
'How dare you interfere with our work? My daughter is a trivial price to pay to reclaim what should have been ours ages ago. Finish the ceremony while I deal with these meddlers!'
'My father was not always like this...I fear that creature is the cause of his madness.'
